Dialogue: 1,0:05:25.01,0:05:29.73,Signs,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\fad(99,1)\bord2\fnArial Black\c&HE77D7E&\3c&HFFF0EF&\fscx70\pos(195.5,323)}Ethics
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.56,0:05:34.23,DefaultItalics,GOTOU,0,0,0,,这简直是单调夜班的最佳消遣。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.23,0:05:35.56,DefaultItalics,GOTOU,0,0,0,,我就暂时不管他们了。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.71,0:05:55.67,DefaultItalics,SASAKI,0,0,0,,结果我昨晚躲起来了。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.67,0:05:58.96,DefaultItalics,SASAKI,0,0,0,,希望田山小姐没有因为我挨骂。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.34,0:06:02.09,DefaultItalics,GOTOU,0,0,0,,别带老头来这里！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.09,0:06:04.72,DefaultItalics,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,对不起我带老头来了。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.84,0:06:07.39,DefaultItalics,GOTOU,0,0,0,,这个礼物我没收了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.39,0:06:09.47,DefaultItalics,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,求您高抬贵手！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.60,0:06:12.18,DefaultItalics,GOTOU,0,0,0,,禁止再抽烟！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.18,0:06:14.27,DefaultItalics,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,太狠心了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.03,0:06:22.24,Signs,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\b0\fs10\bord2\fnTimes New Roman\c&H373737&\3c&HFFFFFF&\frz7.7\fax0.1\pos(314,69)}Melons that\Nyou cut for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.03,0:06:22.24,Signs,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\b0\fs10\bord2\fnTimes New Roman\c&H373737&\3c&HFFFFFF&\frz9.61\fax0.1\pos(348.5,253.5)}I'd eat them every day!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.03,0:06:22.24,Signs,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\fs12\bord2.5\fnArial Black\c&H373737&\3c&HFFFFFF&\frz9.61\fax0.1\pos(252.5,92)}badump
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.08,0:06:34.33,DefaultItalics,GOTOU,0,0,0,,没想到瓜的蔓延会在这里起作用。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.33,0:06:36.50,DefaultItalics,GOTOU,0,0,0,,等不及下一卷了。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.50,0:06:39.25,Signs,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\fs12\c&HFCFCFD&\frz11.31\fscx90\fax0.03\pos(316.5,130)}Return to Library
