Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.42,0:06:41.51,Signs,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\fad(232,1)\fs10\fnComic Sans MS\c&HE3D8B8&\frz12.3\pos(351.5,41)}Catch Me at\Nthe Melon Farm
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.42,0:06:41.51,Signs,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\fad(232,1)\bord2\fs10\fnComic Sans MS\c&HFCFCFC&\frz12.3\pos(359,61.5)\3c&H998FDD&}Nishizono Hanako
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.79,0:06:40.71,DefaultItalics,GOTOU,0,0,0,,好了，接下来看什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.72,0:06:49.56,Default,GOTOU,0,0,0,,怎么了，山田？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.56,0:06:51.27,Default,YAMADA,0,0,0,,哟。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.27,0:06:54.14,Default,GOTOU,0,0,0,,你今天不是只上夜班吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.14,0:06:57.40,Default,YAMADA,0,0,0,,前园店长好像在排班上挺头疼的。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.40,0:06:58.94,Default,YAMADA,0,0,0,,所以我就来了。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.32,0:07:02.69,Default,GOTOU,0,0,0,,你打卡了吧。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.69,0:07:05.03,Default,YAMADA,0,0,0,,打了，肯定打了。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.03,0:07:07.78,Default,GOTOU,0,0,0,,好，真乖。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.78,0:07:12.79,Default,YAMADA,0,0,0,,话说店长，你真戒烟了啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.16,0:07:14.16,Default,GOTOU,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.54,0:07:22.96,Default,GOTOU,0,0,0,,哦，这个权利大多了。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.96,0:07:26.05,Default,GOTOU,0,0,0,,也懒得刷牙喷除臭剂。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.01,0:07:30.68,Default,YAMADA,0,0,0,,可是那是你教我的啊。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.35,0:07:37.98,Default,GOTOU,0,0,0,,行了，你拐弯抹角的想说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.98,0:07:40.65,Default,GOTOU,0,0,0,,有问题就问吧。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.56,0:07:41.32,Signs,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\fad(101,273)\fs27\fnArial Black\c&HFCE3FC&\3c&HE592B6&\bord2\frz19.9\pos(54.5,185)}Yamad'oh
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.48,0:07:47.20,Default,YAMADA,0,0,0,,你还没告诉我抽烟的事行不行。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.20,0:07:51.83,Default,GOTOU,0,0,0,,什么？哦，你是说那老头的事。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.16,0:07:57.00,Default,YAMADA,0,0,0,,我还以为你没报警\N而是直接把他处理掉了。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.00,0:07:58.83,Default,YAMADA,0,0,0,,你没把他埋店后面吧。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.83,0:08:01.71,DefaultItalics,GOTOU,0,0,0,,你想被打哪里？\N选一个吧。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.71,0:08:05.09,DefaultItalics,YAMADA,0,0,0,,哪、哪里都行别打肺！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.09,0:08:07.09,Default,GOTOU,0,0,0,,怎么可能！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.09,0:08:09.30,Default,GOTOU,0,0,0,,你左耳进右耳出是吧。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.30,0:08:12.35,Default,GOTOU,0,0,0,,我说的是「别欺负得太狠」。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.35,0:08:15.35,Default,GOTOU,0,0,0,,换句话说，低调点就行。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.64,0:08:19.77,Default,GOTOU,0,0,0,,那个时间段不影响工作\N我可以睁一只眼闭一只眼。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.77,0:08:22.77,Default,GOTOU,0,0,0,,如果我觉得越界了会叫停。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.86,0:08:27.36,Default,GOTOU,0,0,0,,但除此之外没问题\N就这样。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.15,0:08:30.82,Default,YAMADA,0,0,0,,太幸运了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.57,0:08:32.74,Default,GOTOU,0,0,0,,喂，山田。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.37,0:08:38.12,Default,GOTOU,0,0,0,,出了什么事要马上告诉我。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.21,0:08:43.38,Default,YAMADA,0,0,0,,好的，不过「什么事」是指什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.67,0:08:45.55,Default,GOTOU,0,0,0,,这还用问吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.55,0:08:49.63,Default,GOTOU,0,0,0,,当然是让人心跳加速的事。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.89,0:08:54.85,Default,YAMADA,0,0,0,,好，那我走了。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.35,0:09:05.15,DefaultItalics,SASAKI,0,0,0,,也许我该进去道个歉。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.02,0:09:08.32,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,我只是想表达感谢。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.32,0:09:11.15,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,为什么反而给她添麻烦了呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.15,0:09:12.03,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,喂，擅闯者。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.03,0:09:14.66,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,哇啊！请原谅我！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.74,0:09:17.41,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,等等，田山小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.41,0:09:20.16,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,你鬼鬼祟祟的干嘛呢佐佐木先生。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.04,0:09:25.09,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,前几天在这里遇到了另一个店员。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.09,0:09:27.42,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,你因为我被骂了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.42,0:09:29.67,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,哦，那是店长。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.67,0:09:31.93,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,店、店长？！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.72,0:09:37.01,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,没事，反正你过来吧。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.01,0:09:38.93,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,等等，什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.93,0:09:42.69,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,店、店长同意我在这里抽烟了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.69,0:09:45.69,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,她说低调点就行，没事。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.69,0:09:47.32,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,低调点？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.86,0:09:50.69,DefaultItalics,SASAKI,0,0,0,,这到底是行还是不行？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.84,0:10:10.71,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,还有，佐佐木先生。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.72,0:10:15.05,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,这个真的很可爱。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.22,0:10:21.31,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,我想你不需要我还钱\N但我想表达感谢。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.73,0:10:23.98,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,你喜欢就好。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.98,0:10:24.85,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,我很喜欢。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.36,0:10:32.24,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,看着这个东西我就想笑。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.24,0:10:34.24,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.24,0:10:38.03,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,因为我能想象你在店里挑选的样子。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.87,0:10:43.29,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,等等，为什么会想笑？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.29,0:10:46.79,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,我是说，找到这东西肯定不容易。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.79,0:10:50.00,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,这么可爱的烟灰缸一般地方买不到。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.51,0:11:01.60,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,我能想象你到处问人哪儿有卖。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.27,0:11:05.27,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,而且小商品区总是挤满了女人。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.27,0:11:10.94,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,你会很尴尬地站在那儿挑一个好的。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.03,0:11:18.07,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,田山小姐你真的会读心术吧。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.08,0:11:30.04,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,反正想象那些画面就让我想笑。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.21,0:11:34.67,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,你确定不是拿我当消遣？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.67,0:11:38.55,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,什么啊，不是的\N我是真的觉得心情变好。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.34,0:11:42.31,DefaultItalics,SASAKI,0,0,0,,我永远分不清她是不是认真的。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.36,0:11:52.57,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,谢谢。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.65,0:11:54.86,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,我会珍惜的。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.41,0:12:01.32,DefaultItalics,SASAKI,0,0,0,,我想不管怎样都没关系了。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.32,0:12:03.03,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,喂，佐佐木先生。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.83,0:12:06.33,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,烟灰该弹了。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.33,0:12:09.08,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,哦，你说得对。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.71,0:12:11.59,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,用这个吧。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.34,0:12:16.13,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,真方便呢，谢谢……
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.38,0:12:20.09,DefaultItalics,SASAKI,0,0,0,,这、这个有点近。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.47,0:12:23.10,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,我们不想你被烫到。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.81,0:12:24.85,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,所以，给。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.56,0:12:26.48,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,来。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.85,0:12:28.89,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,呃、呃……
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.89,0:12:32.11,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,能、能直接递给我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.11,0:12:34.48,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,好，拿着吧。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.36,0:12:37.65,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,什……
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.11,0:12:40.78,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,再近一点，快了。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.58,0:12:46.87,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,田山小姐……
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.37,0:12:49.66,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,你为什么在往后退？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.66,0:12:52.13,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,哦，抱歉。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.92,0:12:55.50,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,佐佐木先生你手臂真长啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.50,0:12:57.63,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,给我吧田山小姐。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.63,0:13:00.63,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,趁我手还没断。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.14,0:13:06.56,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,疼……好疼！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.56,0:13:07.31,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.23,0:13:14.65,DefaultItalics,YAMADA,0,0,0,,膏药？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.48,0:13:16.90,DefaultItalics,YAMADA,0,0,0,,难道说……
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.07,0:13:21.28,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,你没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.28,0:13:25.78,Default,YAMADA,0,0,0,,我没事，只是呛了一下。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.78,0:13:29.20,Default,YAMADA,0,0,0,,真的很对不起行了吧。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.20,0:13:32.92,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,你不用道歉啊山田小姐。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.25,0:13:37.09,DefaultItalics,YAMADA,0,0,0,,老头的肌肉酸痛会持续好几天吧。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.38,0:13:40.92,Default,YAMADA,0,0,0,,原谅我佐佐木先生。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.34,0:13:42.80,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,没、没事的！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.30,0:13:45.05,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,没关系山田小姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.05,0:13:45.97,Default,YAMADA,0,0,0,,真的很抱歉。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.97,0:13:47.89,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,别道歉！求你别道歉！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.89,0:13:50.56,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,请不要再道歉了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.93,0:13:51.31,DefaultOverlap,YAMADA,0,0,0,,不，我必须道歉。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.56,0:13:52.94,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,你没有做错任何事！
